_ fix the bugs detected by new tests

_ retrieving a subdirectory should raise "Not Found":  to fix this (in
  gitRetrieve/darcsRetrieve) requires a 'doesFileExist' check in the Nothing case,
  and something fancy with 'git cat-file' to confirm that we have a file for the (Just _) case.

----------

Note:  git will detect renames in "log" and "whatchanged"
if you supply the "-M" flag:

jgm@protagoras:~/tmp/ebo/aaa [26]% git whatchanged
